Aries Stones by Decades
 In addition to the month, you can also take into account the decade in which the person was born:
 1st decade (21.03 - 01.04) - aquamarine, heliotrope, amethyst have a special influence;
 2nd decade (02.04 - 11.04) - diamond (diamond);
 3rd decade (12.04 - 20.04) - emerald, ruby, selenite, bloodstone.

Gemini Stones by Decade
 1st decade (22.05 - 31.05) - emerald, jasper;
 2nd decade (01.06 - 10.06) - rock crystal, garnet, topaz;
 3rd decade (11.06 - 21.06) - pearls, moonstone (for the Gemini woman), sapphire.

Stones of Cancer by decade
 It is believed that talisman stones receive special power if they are selected according to the decade of birth:
 1st decade (22.06 - 01.07) - pearls, moonstone;
 2nd decade (02.07 - 11.07) - emerald, ruby;
 3rd decade (12.07 - 22.07) - moonstone, pearls, ruby.

Lion Stones by Decades
 In addition to the main talisman - ruby, you can recommend an amulet depending on the decade of birth:
 1st decade (from July 23 to August 2) - ruby, chrysolite, heliotrope;
 2nd decade (from August 3 to 12) - diamond (brilliant), topaz;
 3rd decade (from August 13 to 23) - topaz, diamond.

Virgo Stones by Decades of Birth
 In addition to the month of birth, astrologers advise taking into account the decade in which a person was born. 
In this case, Virgo's talismans are:
 1st decade (from August 24 to September 2) - topaz, yellow sapphire;
 2nd decade (from 3 to 12 September) - sapphire, topaz, jasper;
 3rd decade (from September 13 to 22) - sapphire, lapis lazuli.

Stones of Libra by decade of birth
 In addition to the month of birth, astrologers advise taking into account the decade of birth when choosing a talisman stone:
 1st decade (from September 23 to October 9) - diamond, selenite, sapphire;
 2nd decade (from October 4 to October 13) - diamond, amethyst, beryl;
 3rd decade (from October 14 to October 23) - diamond, opal, tiger's eye.

Scorpio Stones by Decades
 Astrologers name additional talismans of Scorpio according to the decade of birth:
 1st decade (from October 24 to November 2) - opal;
 2nd decade (from November 3 to November 13) - ruby;
 3rd decade (from November 14 to November 22) - rock crystal.
